BuildProperties.Value: "{path}/{cmd}" {bootloader.verbose} -s "{path}/share/openocd/scripts/" -f "interface/{protocol}" -c "set telnet_port 0" {extra_params} -f "target/at91samdXX.cfg" -c "telnet_port disabled; init; halt; at91samd bootloader 0; program {{runtime.platform.path}/bootloaders/{bootloader.file}} verify reset; shutdown"

"openocd --version 2>&1 | grep 2016 && if opkg update; then opkg upgrade openocd; exit 1; else echo 'Please connect your board to the Internet in order to upgrade tools' >&2; exit 1; fi || /usr/bin/run-avrdude /tmp/sketch.hex"

"{path}/{cmd}" {bootloader.verbose} -s "{path}/share/openocd/scripts/" -f "{runtime.platform.path}/variants/{build.variant}/{build.openocdscript}" -c "telnet_port disabled; init; halt; at91samd bootloader 0; program {{runtime.platform.path}/bootloaders/{bootloader.file}} verify reset; shutdown"

"{path}/{cmd}" {program.verbose} -s "{path}/share/openocd/scripts/" -f "interface/{protocol}" -c "set telnet_port 0" {extra_params} -f "target/at91samdXX.cfg" -c "telnet_port disabled; program {{build.path}/{build.project_name}.hex} verify reset; shutdown"
